ot taken in a classroom where you were all just casually chatting.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event182-05-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Mhm. If you had submitted them to the photo contest, you might've been a favorite to win~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event182-05-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"lady","body":"Huh?! The Haneoka Photo Contest is still going on?! We started that event when I was on the student council!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"What?! Really?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event182-05-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"That's incredible~! Our girl here 